citeinfo.title: Townships of Iredell County, North Carolina

descript.abstract: A boundary file representing the Townships of Iredell County, North Carolina.
descript.purpose: This data set provides approximate township boundaries and was created to assist governmental agencies and others in making resource management decisions through the use of a Geographic Information System (GIS).

theme.themekt: REQUIRED: Reference to a formally registered thesaurus or a similar authoritative source of theme keywords.
